Scotiabank to Acquire a Portion of Daiwa Securities Brokerage

-- B y   S e a n   B .   P a s t e r n a k
-- 
2011-12-01T19:32:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-01/scotiabank-to-acquire-a-portion-of-daiwa-securities-brokerage.html
Bank of Nova Scotia (BNS) , Canada’s third-
largest bank by assets, agreed to buy a portion of the prime
brokerage of Japan’s  Daiwa Securities Group Inc. (8601)   The bank is buying a technology platform and the size of
the transaction is “small”, Diane Flanagan, a spokeswoman at
the Toronto-based company, said today in an e-mail. The Tokyo
Stock Exchange reported the transaction earlier.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Sean B. Pasternak in Toronto at 
 spasternak@bloomberg.net   To contact the editors responsible for this story:
